    <item>
      <title>Mabel Is No Longer Homophobic</title>
      <author>Tethys_Saturnalia</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/550977</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/550977#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">a20df9e1774ccb8df04281c9006c40b523b8b58a</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 15:52:43 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671bbbec6790a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671bbe82ab2ee.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671bbe82bbacd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod slightly alters Mabel's dialogue so she no longer comments on the player buying clothing intended for the opposite sex.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;When I figured out how to mod dialogue in ACNL, my first thought was to get rid of this awkward-ass dialogue. You are now free to buy whatever you want without the hedgehog judging you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The nitty gritty:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- The lines asking male players if they're buying a present when looking at a skirt or dress have been replaced with some of Mabel's other lines for looking at an item.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- The lines commenting on male players being adventurous or how an item is intended for females when trying on skirts or dresses have been replaced in the same fashion.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- "Oh, talk about boyish and cute!" for female players has been cut down to "Oh, talk about cute!"*&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;*I had a bit of a hard time testing this one, because I don't know what items will make Mabel trigger the "wrong gender" lines for female players. If you encounter this line, please let me know what item it was, and if there was anything unusual about her dialogue, like misplaced line breaks or not asking for confirmation before purchase.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Extra details:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;- English language only - I can read enough to know she's still judging you in Spanish and French, but I do not speak enough to fix it.&lt;br&gt;- Built and tested on NA Welcome amiibo. Other versions' compatibility unknown.&lt;br&gt;- Tested on hardware (Luma) and Citra. Should work the same on both.&lt;br&gt;- This only changes the file relating to Mabel's dialogue inside Able Sisters. Therefore, compatibility with other mods should be pretty good, if not perfect.&lt;br&gt;- Yes, the dialogue's going to get a little repetitive. Sorry.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;If you are here to make disparaging remarks about this mod, me, or the LGBT+ community in&#13;
 any way, shape, or form, you agree that I have the right to vaporize &#13;
you with my laser eyes. (I am warning you in advance that you will be &#13;
immediately deleted and reported. Do not try me.)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/no-judging-mabel_35c0c.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Other/Misc</category>
      <category>Game files</category>
    </item>
